Package: EsoralPrint
Type: Package
Title: EsoralPrint: Platform-Agnostic Scoring for Molecular Interception of Oral and Esophageal Malignancy
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hung-Ming", "Lai", email = "hmlai@aiphaqua.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Implements a scalable, objective, platform-independent, and quantitative measure of 
    the molecular-morphological gap that complements traditional histological grading across OSCC and ESCC.
    It operates on a true single-sample basis, with no need for cross-sample normalization, 
    batch correction, centralized calibration protocols, or strict adherence to inter-sample quality controls. 
